# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:9
translate spanish counselorconversation3_535998b2:

    # pc "There's this girl that lives next door to me, Jamie."
    pc "Hay una chica que vive al lado de mi casa, Jamie."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:10
translate spanish counselorconversation3_dcfcdfa2:

    # pc "I can't get her out of my mind."
    pc "No puedo quitármela de la cabeza."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:11
translate spanish counselorconversation3_bee654f7:

    # sc "You like her?"
    sc "¿Te gusta?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:12
translate spanish counselorconversation3_abd0877e:

    # pc "Yeah, but there's more to it than that."
    pc "Sí, pero hay más que eso."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:13
translate spanish counselorconversation3_c5ac6fea:

    # pc "We have a history. We dated when we were younger, but then I hurt her."
    pc "Tenemos una historia. Salimos juntos cuando éramos más jóvenes, pero luego la hice daño."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:14
translate spanish counselorconversation3_3b37105b:

    # pc "I didn't mean to, but I did."
    pc "No fue mi intención, pero lo hice."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:15
translate spanish counselorconversation3_83b99294:

    # pc "Then I left, and now that I'm back it's sort of like we're starting over, but we still have all this history."
    pc "Luego me fui, y ahora que he vuelto es como si estuviéramos empezando de nuevo, pero seguimos teniendo todo ese pasado."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:18
translate spanish counselorconversation3_af5378b6:

    # pc "Do you know what I mean?"
    pc "¿Sabes a qué me refiero?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:19
translate spanish counselorconversation3_eec64a34:

    # sc "I think I do. You have memories with her, but it's almost like it's a different person because it's been so long."
    sc "Creo que sí. Tienes recuerdos con ella, pero es casi como si fuera una persona diferente porque ha pasado mucho tiempo."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:20
translate spanish counselorconversation3_de5061cc:

    # pc "Exactly! I remember hanging out with her when we were younger, but both of us have changed so much it's sort of like remembering a movie."
    pc "¡Exacto! Recuerdo salir con ella cuando éramos más jóvenes, pero los dos hemos cambiado tanto que es como recordar una película."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:21
translate spanish counselorconversation3_a7dabb45:

    # sc "Does it bother you?"
    sc "¿Te molesta?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:22
translate spanish counselorconversation3_72e3f009:

    # pc "No, not at all."
    pc "No, en absoluto."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:23
translate spanish counselorconversation3_65acc085:

    # pc "It's nice actually. It's like we have a head start."
    pc "De hecho, está bien. Es como si tuviéramos ventaja."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:24
translate spanish counselorconversation3_46d1797b:

    # pc "What happened before isn't holding our relationship back at all. It's really like we just skipped the first couple of levels, you know? Because we already did them."
    pc "Lo que pasó antes no está frenando nuestra relación en absoluto. Es como si nos hubiéramos saltado los primeros niveles, ¿sabes? Porque ya los hemos superado."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:25
translate spanish counselorconversation3_abd28437:

    # sc "So things are getting serious with her?"
    sc "¿Así que las cosas se están poniendo serias con ella?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:26
translate spanish counselorconversation3_ee1883b8:

    # pc "I don't know if I'd call it serious, but we both like each other."
    pc "No sé si lo llamaría serio, pero nos gustamos."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:27
translate spanish counselorconversation3_d72f2f51:

    # sc "Companionship is good. You should have somebody in your life that you can rely on."
    sc "La compañía es buena. Deberías tener a alguien en tu vida en quien puedas confiar."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:28
translate spanish counselorconversation3_7d69eb5d:

    # sc "Somebody who makes you happy."
    sc "Alguien que te haga feliz."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:30
translate spanish counselorconversation3_1487ed22:

    # "Her voice suddenly takes on a somber tone as she says this, as if she does not have that someone."
    "Su voz adquiere de repente un tono sombrío al decir esto, como si ella no tuviera a esa persona."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:31
translate spanish counselorconversation3_5d687698:

    # "But you've seen the ring on her finger, you know that she's married."
    "Pero has visto el anillo en su dedo, sabes que está casada."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:35
translate spanish counselorconversation3_3c7fbaef:

    # sc "Oh, yes I'm fine."
    sc "Oh, sí, estoy bien."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:39
translate spanish counselorconversation3_fa2bc12a:

    # sc "Good, I'm happy for you."
    sc "Bien, me alegro por ti."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:41
translate spanish counselorconversation3_fc38e4d4:

    # sc "Well it's about time for you to get to class."
    sc "Bueno, ya es hora de que vayas a clase."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:42
translate spanish counselorconversation3_a8c43555:

    # pc "Okay, I'll see you next time Gertrude."
    pc "Vale, nos vemos la próxima vez, Gertrude."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:43
translate spanish counselorconversation3_1b784c07:

    # sc "Bye, [pcname]."
    sc "Adiós, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:44
translate spanish counselorconversation3_e4b88e88:

    # "With that, I stand up and head to class."
    "Con eso, me levanto y me dirijo a clase."

